
ic:(?ExprX < ?ExprY)

   ExprX is strictly less than ExprY.

Arguments
   ExprX               Arithmetic expression
   ExprY               Arithmetic expression

Type
   library(ic)

Description

   Constrains ExprX to be strictly less than ExprY.
